<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Central do Cliente</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000, #1a1a1a);
        color: #ffffff;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
        text-align: center;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,191,255,0.2);
        max-width: 420px;
        animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);}
        to {opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
    }

    h1 {
        color: #00bfff;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    p {
        color: #ccc;
        font-size: 15px;
    }

    .botao {
        display: block;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 14px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00bfff, #009acd);
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .botao:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00bfff;
    }

    .whatsapp-btn {
        display: block;
        margin: 10px auto;
        padding: 12px;
        background: #25D366;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .whatsapp-btn:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #25D366;
    }

    .rodape {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
    }
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Central do Cliente</h1>

    <p>Acesse suas faturas, consulte informações e mantenha tudo em dia de forma rápida e segura.</p>

    <a class="botao" href="https://yayu.sgp.tsmx.com.br/accounts/central/login" target="_blank">
        🔐 Acessar Faturas
    </a>

    <p>Precisa de ajuda? Fale com nosso suporte:</p>

    <a class="whatsapp-btn" href="https://wa.me/5513988777008" target="_blank">
        💬 Falar no WhatsApp
    </a>

    <div class="rodape">
        Atendimento rápido • Seguro • Profissional
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
